      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELSA ABOVE (1) finished in the minors last start over the 527m at this track but ran a handy 30.45 last start. Has the ability and expected to go close again. CANYA BREW IT (8) turned in a solid run fresh when finishing in the placings at this track in a Grade 4/5 (25.09). Will strip fitter for the run. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Expected to be in the finish again. SAMMY'S BEACH (2) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fourth (31.11) at this track in a Grade 5. Expected to do much better this time. GIVE A LITTLE (6) has strong claims after a top-three finish in good time last time out.",
